thread.title: Soap | Red Rock

author: Fiona Flynn
title: Soap | Red Rock
text: Tommy is still furious with Conor after his dabble with drink the night before and soon realises the shining Conor is taking to Rachel and warns him off. Looks like we may have a new forbidden romance brewing in Red Rock. Over at the station, the Gardai are still trying to work out who was behind Davey's stabbing and, still fuming from their belongings being stolen at the football match, Adrijan and Sean pay Keith Kiely a visit – despite McKay’s instructions to put it behind them in the interest of community spirit. Will Keith come up trumps for the boys in blue?
